data.description: MAJOR PRICE DROP! Now only $187 per square foot! Come see this updated home in the coveted Wildwood subdivision. This north facing home is close to highly rated schools and many of the other great options in Bentonville and Rogers. The home has a great formal dining room moving seemlessly into the living area and kitchen area. There is a huge backyard and patio area including a beautiful sunroom that add to the ambiance of the home. The roof and hot water heater have been recently replaced. Upgrades in the home include main level flooring and quartz counter tops. All kitchen appliances have been replaced within the last year. Upstairs you will find three large bedrooms with walk-in closets that will serve the needs of a large family. This home is within walking distance to the community center. There are also several great areas that would make a wonderful home office.
